		nav.landing-nav
				a.active(href="/") Home
				a(href='/') About Us 
				a(href='http://blog.getlatch.com/') Blog
		.vertical
				.inner
					.blog-logo
						img(src='/images/logo3.png', alt='Latch Logo')
					//- h1.blog-title Latch
					h2.blog-description Multi-family residences go keyless.

					.signup-blurb Signup to learn more:
